OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1778191868
OL,3,CWoman in her 20s allegedly raped and
OL,4,Cassaulted by Redheugh Bridge in
OL,5,CGateshead
OL,7,FA woman has been allegedly assaulted
OL,8,Fand raped by a man unknown to her in
OL,9,FGateshead.
OL,11,FNorthumbria Police are asking people
OL,12,Ffor any dash cam footage or
OL,13,Finformation if they were in the
OL,14,FRedheugh Bridge area between 1:20am
OL,15,Fand 2:10am on Saturday (2 May).
OL,17,FOfficers say the suspect is described
OL,18,Fas a tall, white man with blonde hair
OL,19,Fand a local accent. He is believed to
OL,20,Fbe in his 20s.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
