PN,42502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1778191868
OL,3,CWoman in her 20s allegedly raped and
OL,4,Cassaulted by Redheugh Bridge in
OL,5,CGateshead
OL,7,FThe woman, in her 20s, went to a safe
OL,8,Fplace after the incident at the
OL,9,Fbridge's junction with Askew Road and
OL,10,Fthen police were contacted.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Chris
OL,13,FDeavin, of Northumbria Police's
OL,14,FSafeguarding team, said: "Firstly, I
OL,15,Fwant to recognise the bravery of the
OL,16,Fvictim and we will continue to offer
OL,17,Fthem any specialist support we can.
OL,19,F"As soon as we received the report, we
OL,20,Fbegan an investigation and have been
OL,21,Fcarrying out extensive enquiries.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
