PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1778191868
OL,3,CWoman in her 20s allegedly raped and
OL,4,Cassaulted by Redheugh Bridge in
OL,5,CGateshead
OL,7,F"We are now appealing to the public
OL,8,Ffor help and asking anyone who was in
OL,9,Fthe area at the time and saw anything
OL,10,Fsuspicious to come forward.
OL,12,F"If you do have any information ` no
OL,13,Fmatter how insignificant you think it
OL,14,Fmay be ` please do contact us, as it
OL,15,Fcould assist with our enquiries.
OL,17,F"We are committed to bringing
OL,18,Fperpetrators of these types of crimes
OL,19,Fto justice."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
